Test (EnvMatch Sky_Theme skywall) *FvwmShelf: (22x2, Frame 0)
Test (!EnvMatch Sky_Panels_Type 1.6) *FvwmShelf: (22x10, Swallow "Shelf-FvwmPager" "Module FvwmPager Shelf-FvwmPager *")
Test (!EnvMatch Sky_Panels_Type 1.6) *FvwmShelf: (22x1, Frame 0)
*FvwmShelf: (22x4, Frame 0, Swallow stalonetray `Exec exec stalonetray --geometry 8x2 --max-geometry 5x2 --grow-gravity=SE --icon-gravity=NW --icon-size=16 --no-shrink --parent-bg`)
*FvwmShelf: (22x2, Frame 0, Padding 36 0, Left, Swallow "FvwmClockApplet" `Module FvwmScript $[Sky_Dir]/fvwmscript.clockapplet-mod.rc`)


